### Implemented -concise flag that reduces the noise in the output of plan

Instead of adding another ViewType like HumanView or JsonView, I chose to add a bool flag for concise within the global View that takes care of compact warnings and no colour so that in future if a concise mode needs to be
```go
// The PlanHuman implementation renders human-readable text logs, suitable for
// a scrolling terminal.
type PlanHuman struct {
	view *View
	concise bool
	inAutomation bool
}
```

